Company Profile:Squalet (www.squalet.com) is
a fast growing online health and beauty shopping site based in Singapore. We
are a start-up that aims to expand to become one of the biggest health and
beauty e-commerce in Singapore. You will be sharing your ideas and be part of
an innovative, motivated and fast-paced team.
Job Description:Main responsibilities
·      Help to launch one of the biggest health and beauty
online ventures in Singapore·      Take responsibilities in the development of products ·      Support in Sales & Marketing, Operations and
Finance on various tasks·      Interact and provide insightful ideas to top
managementWho we are looking for
The ideal candidate is
energetic, self-motivated, hardworking and should have the desire to work in an
entrepreneurial environment. The ideal candidate possesses the following
background:·      Students or fresh grads, Singaporeans or foreigners
with a valid working visa may apply·      Strong educational background with outstanding
academic grades·      Interest in the internet space·      Strong analytical and communication skill·      Interest to work in a start-up: Fast-paced, take on
heavy responsibilities, contribute ideas and may require long hoursWhat to expect
You can expect an entrepreneurial
business environment as well as the opportunity to be part of the development
of a fast-growing company. You can take on real responsibilities and benefit
from our flexibility, motivation and high learning curve. In Squalet, we are
open to your contribution of new ideas.
